name: Art Is Basically An Excitement
description: Do you believe that Gedung SR's pillars have ears? Suddenly I miss Mr. Anto, asked for help to tell Ocul to clean the mess at the Anduslasia and being asked about broken pieces of beer bottle on Lapmer. Since Arno likes to disturb me and Bintang while chilling on Lapmer stairs to preach about how important Propganda is, it feels like seeing the Gedung SR can't be like an ordinary building anymore, but more like a subject who's always be dressed up to surprise people. Despite that, the feeling of Gedung SR at 7 am is not as good as when it's 5 am.
